                            <cell>Budget increased by reason of reorganization under decree No. 1427
                                of 1917</cell>
                            <cell role="num">$337,644.00</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Repairs to schoolship <hi rend="italic">Patria</hi> and gunboat
