                    <p rend="center">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Additional Cost</hi>
                    </p>
                    <table cols="2" rows="2">
                        <row>
                            <cell>Increased police force</cell>
                            <cell role="num">$730,325.92</cell>
                        </row>
                        <row>
                            <cell>Cost of increased harbor police</cell>
                            <cell role="num">24,500.00</cell>
                        </row>
                    </table>
                    <p>One million dollars has already been advanced to the Cuba Railroad, and an
                        additional $2,000,000 will be loaned to that Company, making a total of
                        $3,000,000.</p>
                    <p>An advance has been made to the Cuban Eastern Railway Company of $93,000.</p>
                    <p rend="center">
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Recapitulation</hi>
                    </p>
                    <table cols="2" rows="6">
